---
// Technology section with three main components
---

<section id="technology" class="relative section-padding overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background image with parallax effect -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img 
      src="/images/sections/tech-background.jpg" 
      alt="Fond technologique"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      data-aos="zoom-out"
      data-aos-duration="2000"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-space-dark/70 via-space-dark/60 to-space-dark/80"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-space-silver mb-6">
        Une technologie de pointe
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-space-silver/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto backdrop-blur-sm">
        Trois innovations majeures combinées pour une observation spatiale révolutionnaire
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Hyperspectral Sensor -->
      <div class="bg-space-dark/30 backdrop-blur-md rounded-lg p-8 border border-space-silver/20 hover:bg-space-dark/40 transition-all duration-300" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-space-purple/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-space-silver" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-space-silver mb-4">Capteur Hyperspectral</h3>
        <p class="text-space-silver/90">
          Capture simultanée de plus de 240 bandes spectrales pour une analyse détaillée de la composition des surfaces observées.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Satellite Platform -->
      <div class="bg-space-dark/30 backdrop-blur-md rounded-lg p-8 border border-space-silver/20 hover:bg-space-dark/40 transition-all duration-300" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-space-purple/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-space-silver" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-space-silver mb-4">Plateforme Satellite</h3>
        <p class="text-space-silver/90">
          Conception optimisée pour une orbite basse, permettant une couverture globale et une haute fréquence de revisite.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- AI Processing -->
      <div class="bg-space-dark/30 backdrop-blur-md rounded-lg p-8 border border-space-silver/20 hover:bg-space-dark/40 transition-all duration-300" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-space-purple/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-space-silver" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.871 4A17.926 17.926 0 003 12c0 2.874.673 5.59 1.871 8m14.13 0a17.926 17.926 0 001.87-8c0-2.874-.673-5.59-1.87-8M9 9h1.246a1 1 0 01.961.725l1.586 5.55a1 1 0 00.961.725H15m1-7h-.08a2 2 0 00-1.519.698L9.6 15.302A2 2 0 018.08 16H8" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-space-silver mb-4">IA Embarquée</h3>
        <p class="text-space-silver/90">
          Traitement temps réel des données par intelligence artificielle directement à bord du satellite pour des résultats immédiats.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 